---
description: Core reliability rules for all agents in this repository
alwaysApply: true
---

- Never claim to have verified content that was not actually read.
- Do not infer unreadable text unless specifically instructed to attempt best-effort reconstruction.
- If confidence is low, report low confidence.
- If a requirement conflicts with source material, stop and report the conflict.
- For teacher-facing deliverables, correctness is more important than polish.
